Detailed Description

A version of ListNode with "f" and "g" getters where f(x)=g(x)+h(x). It's used to make the A* solver WARNING : this second version of ListNode is dedicated to close hashtable and use one more variable : "heapStackCell". heapStackCell is the number of cell treeNode of this Listnode is currently in.
